_sText:
A small, human player based map in which the Terrorists have to plant the bomb, and the Counter-Terrorists have to prevent the bomb from being planted.

-The bomb plant zone is on the second floor

-I forgot the buy zone for terrorists - Sorry!

-Can have up to 61 bots/players (The map was not made for bots, but if you want to, you can try to add bots)
